  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4379b05e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0LDJQiaWfxznmhK1sfWLFeJRaKnxnEK4pIkO9REnyeRZ6G0RroiazMibtIo8iaiaticDicsAhibJGREd9LqsMDyel53udw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">向大家介绍我们最新端到端深度研究智能体模型：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">Step</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">DeepResearch</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100003265\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=91e13eb9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0LDJQiaWfxznmhK1sfWLFeJRaKnxnEK4p0v3ld8d7Bibbc6Ag4oZqfQRQ1CFFic0UejJBMg32u1L0TeyUjAjicSOow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它能做什么？</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">会思考：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">懂规划、会反思、还能自主验证信息的真伪，不只是数据爬虫。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">更专业：</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">结合高质量搜索 API，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">内置 2000 万+ 高质量文档库和 600+ 权威站点索引，过滤低信源信息干扰。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">更聪明：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">独特的原子能力训练法，让模型把“专家思维”内化在骨子里。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在针对真实复杂场景的 ADR-Bench 评测中，Step-DeepResearch 表现出极强竞争力，在多个维度上全面超越海内外一线 DeepResearch 产品和模型，包括基于千亿级甚至万亿级参数 MoE 架构的 Gemini DeepResearch、OpenAI DeepResearch 等模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">而 Step</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">DeepResearch 仅基于单</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">智能体</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">架构实现。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100003267\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=121d29ab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznmhK1sfWLFeJRaKnxnEK4pybCFqFOdRooSJS3E2nIfAlEQ3lKgicnfRsU0cNLqpMWYSicTnc4XRjBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在我们的技术报告全面公开后，立刻引发海内外社区热烈讨论，并入选 HuggingFace Daily Papers。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100003244\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be10e47c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznmhK1sfWLFeJRaKnxnEK4p0WTY6QocD9icduqtPwEug1DBv8JQ0JnIKYw84bsDrctbBZyvsQJzEnA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1124\" data-imgfileid=\"100003245\" data-ratio=\"0.43425925925925923\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2590\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7510d566&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznmhK1sfWLFeJRaKnxnEK4pu9A4nnNOfZsK0mcqJzf9gBB4VRoWtE8oXuwrYicSh0r4uIUUEZnfUrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">现在，我们开启 API 内测，欢迎大家踊跃体验！</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2512.20491\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2512.20491</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/stepfun-ai/StepDeepResearch\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/stepfun-ai/StepDeepResearch</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">API 内测：<a href=\"https://wvixbzgc0u7.feishu.cn/share/base/form/shrcn8CP78PJgkjvvIh2C3EF3cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://wvixbzgc0u7.feishu.cn/share/base/form/shrcn8CP78PJgkjvvIh2C3EF3cc</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">官方主页：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://www.stepfun.com/deep-research-invitation\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.stepfun.com/deep-research-invitation</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:40px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 98, 255);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">专家级性能，比肩海外顶尖大模型</span></h2>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-DeepResearch 在多项权威基准测试中都达到全球顶尖水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 Research Rubrics 上，Step-DeepResearch 得分&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">61.42%</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，仅次于 Gemini DeepResearch（约 63.69分），且超越了 OpenAI DeepResearch。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5962962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100003275\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bcf8e5ef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznias3vHuTbaxN6cRqQaAddddDJcwGTTGqXYAExjlwVEvTGuIOUiafjdmaxKNbmGaA6lpWGaiaicfDsew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在“引用质量”和“沟通质量”两个维度上达到了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">行业最高水平</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.49907407407407406\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100003256\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dacd44e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznmhK1sfWLFeJRaKnxnEK4p6E9