p: break-word !important;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\">\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px;border-color: rgb(160, 160, 160);visibility: visible;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/0LDJQiaWfxznias3vHuTbaxN6cRqQaAdddMB0eoqSz5fNBjI0E1xvuHaBvMTmFBSM7YOrdbqicqma47hsTwib9Nb1A/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"563\" data-cropsely2=\"8580\" data-imgfileid=\"100003274\" data-ratio=\"15.225836431226766\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;width: 662px !important;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1076\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c87359af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0LDJQiaWfxznias3vHuTbaxN6cRqQaAdddMB0eoqSz5fNBjI0E1xvuHaBvMTmFBSM7YOrdbqicqma47hsTwib9Nb1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(160, 160, 160);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 16px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">▲上下滑动查看详细内容</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:40px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 98, 255);font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">让基础模型快速成为深度研究专家</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step-DeepResearch 的主要创新可归纳为3方面：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于原子能力的数据合成策略</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">渐进式智能体训练范式</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">自建 ADR-Bench 评估体系</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们将深度研究能力拆分为四个原子能力，并针对性地合成数据进行强化。</span></span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">规划与任务拆解：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能将模糊、宏大的用户需求拆解为可执行的子任务，并根据环境反馈动态调整路径。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">深度信息搜索：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">具备多跳推理能力，能在信息不完整时进行“主动拓扑行走”，挖掘隐藏实体。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">反思与验证：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">拥有“自纠错”和“事实核查”能力，能识别自身错误并区分网络信息的真伪，通过跨源验证确保逻辑严密。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">报告生成：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过中期训练（Mid-training）学习专家写作风格，并利用 SFT 确保报告严格遵循规划结构和引用规范。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">我们的智能体训练范式主要包含三个阶段：</span></span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Agentic Mid-training：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在预训练和微调之间加入 Mid-training，通过 32K 和 128K 两个阶段的上下文调度，注入原子能力，使模型内化“下一步行动”的决策逻辑，而非简单的“预测下一个 Token”。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SFT</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">侧重于长程决策轨迹的合成与领域适配，强化意图理解、规划执行及严格引用格式的遵循，解决模型在长时间研究任务中容易“分心”或“迷路”的问题。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">RL：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">引入 Checklist-style Judger 奖励设计，将复杂的报告质量评估转化为细粒度的信号，进一步优化长程决策的鲁棒性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在系统架构上，我们采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">单智能体 ReAct 架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，避免复杂多智能体系统协作带来的系统冗余。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100003258\" data-ratio=\"0.4046296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31357ec0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0LDJQiaWfxznmhK1sfWLFeJRaKnxnEK4pXfvnlengiclWLOnfzcKYPibhhaufRuutX9sibicj911hFXVC47Cg9rBtZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，为了填补中文深度研究评估的空白，我们还构建了&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">ADR-Bench</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，涵盖商业调研、政策分析、软件工程等 9 大领域，包含通用和专业（法律、金融）两个维度。该基准测试不仅关注搜索结果是否正确，更加关注研究过程中的逻辑严密性、意图识别深度以及长程决策的鲁棒性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">欢迎与我们讨论交流，共同推动 DeepResearch 发展！</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"396\" data-imgfileid=\"100003251\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"width: 191px;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"396\" data-width=\"396\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb690d1c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0LDJQiaWfxznmhK1sfWLFeJRaKnxnEK4pPu7qfCtXLnxLa9Frx79kXFVxemXPZlj8GK1zEsZOzfaXAsA6urShIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阶跃星辰发布 Step-DeepResearch 深度研究智能体，通过原子能力训练和渐进式智能体范式，实现比肩顶尖模型的专家级调研能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阶跃星辰发布 Step-DeepResearch 深度研究智能体，通过原子能力训练和渐进式智能体范式，实现比肩顶尖模型的专家级调研能力。",
  "summary": "阶跃星辰正式上线 Step-DeepResearch，这是一款端到端的深度研究智能体模型。该模型在 ADR-Bench 等多项评测中表现优异，引用与沟通质量达到行业领先水平，且在单智能体架构下实现了极高的成本效益。技术核心在于三方面创新：基于原子能力（规划、搜索、反思、生成）的数据合成策略、包含 Agentic Mid-training 在内的三阶段渐进式训练范式，以及自建的 ADR-Bench 评估体系。该模型旨在解决长程决策中的“分心”问题，提供具备专家思维的深度调研报告。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "采用原子能力拆解与针对性数据合成策略。",
      "explanation": "将深度研究拆分为规划拆解、深度搜索、反思验证和报告生成四个核心能力，通过合成数据强化模型在复杂任务中的专家思维。"
    },
    {
      "point": "创新的渐进式智能体训练范式（Agentic Mid-training）。",
      "explanation": "在预训练和微调间加入 Mid-training 阶段，使模型内化决策逻辑而非简单的 Token 预测，提升长程决策的鲁棒性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "坚持单智能体 ReAct 架构以提升效率。",
      "explanation": "相比复杂的多智能体协作系统，单智能体架构有效避免了系统冗余，在保持高性能的同时显著降低了推理成本。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
